id: psa_crypto_rsa_crypt_legacy
package: platform
label: Legacy RSA Encryption
description: >-
  This component adds support for asymmetric encryption using the legacy RSA
  scheme as specified in RSA Labratories' PKCS #1 specification v1.5. If
  possible, it's recommended to use PSA-OAEP.
category: Platform|Security|PSA Crypto|Asymmetric Encryption
quality: evaluation

provides:
  - name: psa_crypto_rsa_crypt_legacy
  - name: psa_crypto_rsa_crypt
    allow_multiple: true

requires:
  - name: psa_crypto_rsa
  - name: mbedtls_pkcs1_v15

template_contribution:
  - name: psa_crypto_config
    value: PSA_WANT_ALG_RSA_PKCS1V15_CRYPT 1
metadata:
  sbom:
    license: Apache-2.0
    upstream:
      name: Mbed TLS
      version: v3.6.2
      supplier: Trusted Firmware
      url: https://github.com/Mbed-TLS/mbedtls.git
      comment: Mbed TLS is a C library implementing the PSA Cryptography API, cryptographic primitives, X.509 certificate manipulation and the SSL/TLS and DTLS protocols
